kitchens.description:
A Place for Food Entrepreneurs

Shared Commercial / Commissary kitchen for rent. We are a Commercial Kitchen that offers shared rental space to Chefs and other Industry Professionals. We have 2 ovens, 2 stock pot burners, a flat top grill and a 4 burner cook top. We also have a walk in cooler and freezer, 20 qt mixer, warming ovens, and more. A perfect space to operate your ghost kitchen or food prep for your food truck We offer hourly rates with no minimum. Call or text Lisa to schedule a tour. Hourly and monthly rates available. No minimum and no long term contract. Even better than a ghost kitchen!!
